title: WordPress Web Application Development
description:
English | ISBN: 1783280751 | 2013 | 376 pages | PDF | 5 MB 

Developing WordPress-powered websites is one of the standout trends in the modern web development world. 

The flexibility and power of the built-in features offered by WordPress has made developers turn their attentions to the possibility of using it as a web development framework.

This book will act as a comprehensive resource for building web applications with this amazing framework.
